snippet.title: Sinister Squidward | A SpongeBob Horror Game Trailer 2023
snippet.description:
What would happen if Squidward finally went insane and decided to wreak havoc on the residents of Bikini Bottom? 

Take control of the mean cashier as he transforms into a menacing monster, then play as Sandy to save Spongebob and Patrick from this tentacle horror!

Download the game on Itch:  https://rinbash.itch.io/sinister-squidward

This is a horror/comedy fan game based on the characters from the Spongebob Squarepants franchise which is owned by Viacom International.
